graph TD
    Operation[Operation] --> Try{Try Block}
    Try -->|Success| Result[Return Result]
    Try -->|Error| Catch{Catch Error}
    Catch -->|Recoverable| Retry{Retry?}
    Catch -->|Fatal| LogError[Log Error]
    Retry -->|Yes| Operation
    Retry -->|No| Fallback[Use Fallback]
    LogError --> Alert[Send Alert]
    Alert --> Terminate[Terminate]
    Fallback --> Result
